track_notes: There is room for a few cars in the dip at spot height 212. This route takes you over Wainwrights Longlands Fell (LDW-179) Brae Fell (LDW-134) Great Sca Fell (LDW-114) KNOTT, Meal Fell LDW-148 and Great Cockup LDW-159. If you had an early start and have energy left you could drive the short distance to Binsey LD-041 and activate that also.
track_title: Knott and 5 Wainwrights in the Uldale Fells
